Created a workflow JSON for the entity Mail based on the functional requirements:

- Initial state "created" transitions to "validated"
- In "validated", two conditional transitions based on isHappy: to "sendHappy" or "sendGloomy"
- "sendHappy" state processes sendHappyMail processor and transitions to "completed"
- "sendGloomy" state processes sendGloomyMail processor and transitions to "completed"
- "completed" state has no transitions

The workflow JSON is saved to src/main/java/com/java_template/application/workflow/Mail.json.